        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your <em>warmask</em> sharpens your connection to the source of your mask's power. During your daily preparations, choose @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Fear], @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Phantom Pain], or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sure Strike].</p>\n<p>Until your next daily preparations, you can cast this spell as a 1st-rank innate spell once per day; the spell's tradition is determined by the tradition tied to your <em>warmask</em>. You must be wearing your <em>warmask</em> to Cast the Spell.</p>"
